cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for segmenting sub-cortical structures of the human brain in MR image data. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as well as machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of Markov Random Fields (MRF) for improving segmentation results, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
